A state of active radar system within lives
===========================================
Each and every humans being have senses/ mind/ observation/realization/understanding..so on  towards self or towards others, little or more,lower intensity or higher intensity,
distributed or centralized and these activities are always in active/transmission state. The base of these activities are the waves and intensity of waves or in other words the state of energy within us.
Every waves start perceiving just after its construction. The affinity towards stability of the source decide the perceiving direction/nature of waves.
Our sources waves like senses/ mind/ observation/ realization/ understanding construct the waves and the same get engage towards the direction where we feel more stability at first site.

Ex-
When we trow a stone in water, a wave get created and the instance wave of water move towards shore since its get affinity to stabilize the source water(pond).

In case of human being also the same process follow by the waves get created in our mind/body/heart/intellect and on first site it also perceive towards the direction where the source get stability but it is our poor understanding who teasing the movement of waves at intermediate state and every games get started from here.

How one stop teasing the waves?
--------------------------------------------
If you want to stop teasing of waves simply on surface of mind then it will create another state of teasing and this state is not for stop the teasing of first level of waves but it will try to fulfill the wishes(another waves) that get created in your mind. So your force/wishes/poor understanding never work to stop teasing of waves once it get created.

Ex-
Let us you throw a stone(S1) in pond and a waves(W1) get created, it will automatically perceive in the direction where it realize the stability of pond water, No need to do here anything here except observation.It is your poor understanding(P1) who try to turn the direction of waves for that it throw another stone(S2) for turning the wave(W1) direction but what happen S2 again create another wave(W2). Here W2 not in position to stop W1 but it interfere the natural propagation of W1..similar way again S3,S4 for turning of W2..so on...finally you makes a circular track on which you get stuck during rotation.

If our understanding get at the state of observation then we can look the what is happening in our mind, for what a waves get created in our mind using external source,
we have caliber to intercept our activity lightly but never try to stop it/never try to fight with it/never try to teasing it since every waves is energy and its the nature of waves/energy to keep its state in streaming towards the stability of source.

***Observation system is a special design/structure of collections of waves structure that can interact the different states of waves***

Our observation system can simply look/just trace the waves.It is just like from where it get created and from where it get affinity for stability of its source of creation.
What stability try to achieve by source of mind/feeling/intellect by using these waves.

Observation system have caliber to just observe the activity of waves and intensity of waves. It never touch or interfere the propagation of waves. Max to max it intercept the activities of waves or its streaming of intensity.

***Observation system is nothing but the radar system engages with self's activities/waves***
***Senses/mind is a poor radar system that mostly engages with others activities/waves***

